.TH VARIABLE 9
.SH NAME
variable \- interrogate a radiobutton variable
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f5variable \fIvar\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B Variable
returns the value of a Tk radiobutton variable.
An error diagnostic will be returned if
the variable is of the wrong type (if for instance
it is the name of a named channel).
.PP
The special variable
.B lasterror
gives the text of the last Tk error encountered.
It resets when queried.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IR radiobutton (9)
